'''Foxmail'''是[[腾讯公司|腾讯公司]]旗下的[[免费软件|免费]][[电子邮件客户端|电子邮件客户端]]，具有[[電子郵件|電子郵件]]管理<ref>《常用工具软件》第二版,吴文虎、李秋弟、赵红梅著, 全国信息技术及应用远程培训教育工作组2005年出版 第180页</ref>和邮件服务器功能<ref>《Foxmail 5.0实用教程》，植国贤著，清华大学出版社2004年出版</ref>。同时它还有[[RSS|RSS]]订阅、[[日历|日历]]、[[通讯录|联系人]]等功能。

== 歷史 ==
Foxmail最初在1997年1月由[[华中科技大学|华中科技大学]]毕业生[[張小龍|張小龍]]開發，其名字取自[[金庸|金庸]]武侠小说《[[笑傲江湖|笑傲江湖]]》中的人物[[令狐冲|令狐冲]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://tech.sina.com.cn/2018-10-31/doc-ihnfikvc7281920.shtml |title=张小龙悼念金庸:foxmail名字源于金庸小说人物令狐冲 |accessdate=2018-10-31 |archive-date=2018-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181031133051/https://tech.sina.com.cn/2018-10-31/doc-ihnfikvc7281920.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2000年4月18日，Foxmail以1200萬元的價格賣給了[[博大公司|博大公司]]，随后于2005年3月16日被[[腾讯控股|腾讯控股]]收购<ref name="acquired">Xu Caixing. "Now that Tencent has Acquired Foxmail, What are the Plans of Zhang Xiaolong, the Developer of QQ?"  ''<span>[PConline.com.cn PConline.com.cn]</span>''.  PConline.  18 March 2005.  Retrieved at <http://news.pconline.com.cn/hy/0503/577240.html {{Wayback|url=http://news.pconline.com.cn/hy/0503/577240.html |date=20110823053147 }}> on 2 June 2011. (Chinese).</ref>。

== 使用 ==
根据2001年[[新浪网|新浪网]]的统计，Foxmail在中国占有32.92%的市场份额<ref>"Interview with Zhang Xiaolong: Foxmail 4.0 is Still Free".  ''SINA.com.cn''.  Stone Rich Sight.  24 September 2001.  Retrieved at <http://tech.sina.com.cn/c/2001-08-24/5372.html {{Wayback|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/c/2001-08-24/5372.html |date=20110928064438 }}> on 2 June 2011.  (Chinese).</ref>。在2003年的一份与[[威瑞信|威瑞信]]共同发布的推广[[国际化域名|国际化域名]]的新闻稿中透露Foxmail在中国每天有超过300万用户<ref>"VeriSign Breaks the English Language Hold On Internet Navigation With Internationalized Domain Names" ''VeriSign.com''.  VeriSign.  4 March 2003.  Retrieved at <http://www.verisign.com/static/002497.pdf {{Wayback|url=http://www.verisign.com/static/002497.pdf |date=20070928002927 }}> on 2 June 2011.</ref>，而作为对比，2002年1月中国互联网用户的总数为3500万<ref name="HughesWacker2003">{{cite book|author1=Hughes, Christopher R.|author2=Wacker, Gudrun|title=China and the Internet: politics of the digital leap forward|url=https://archive.org/details/chinainternetpol00hugh|url-access=|year=2003|publisher=Routeledge|isbn=978-0-415-27772-3|page=[https://archive.org/details/chinainternetpol00hugh/page/n45 31]}}</ref>。Foxmail的教程经常可以在面向中国市场的互联网扫盲书籍中找到<ref name="李伟郑岩峰2005">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9iKZ4J91gngC&pg=PA159 |title=工具软件实用培训教程/实用培训教程系列 |last2=Zheng Yanfeng |last3=Fang Jun |publisher=清华大学出版社 |year=2005 |isbn=978-7-302-10036-2 |pages=159–168 |author1=Li Wei |access-date=2019-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101123243/http://books.google.com/books?id=9iKZ4J91gngC&pg=PA159 |archive-date=2014-01-01 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="正洪乔武滇葛2005">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7EILUBR0lSUC&pg=PA94 |title=Internet教学应用("校校通工程"丛书) |last2=Wu Diange |publisher=Qinghua University Press |year=2005 |isbn=978-7-302-11021-7 |pages=94–105 |author1=Zheng Hongqiao |access-date=2019-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101123155/http://books.google.com/books?id=7EILUBR0lSUC&pg=PA94 |archive-date=2014-01-01 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="王定陈波2005">{{cite book|author1=Wang Ding|author2=Chen Bo|title=A Concise Internet Tutorial (Internet简明教程)|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-ga0y3mq_RMC&pg=PA99|year=2005|publisher=Qinghua University Press|isbn=978-7-302-10881-8|pages=99–107|access-date=6 December 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101123245/http://books.google.com/books?id=-ga0y3mq_RMC&pg=PA99|archive-date=2014-01-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="康昱陈泽友2008">{{cite book|author1=Kang Yu|author2=Chen Zeyou|title=An Introduction to Home Computer Use: Increasing Proficiency (家庭电脑应用入门·提高·精通)|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1nIiOOSDJ_wC&pg=PA214|year=2008|publisher=DynoMedia Inc.|isbn=978-7-111-22707-6|pages=214–217|access-date=6 December 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101123251/http://books.google.com/books?id=1nIiOOSDJ_wC&pg=PA214|archive-date=2014-01-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 争议 ==
荷兰版[[PC_Magazine|PC Magazine]]报道称，Foxmail的6.0版本偶尔会向datacollect.foxmail.com.cn发送电子邮件使用数据，但总体来说是“优秀的电子邮件客户端”，推荐不受此问题影响的被腾讯收购前的最后一个版本，即5.0.8版<ref>Joost Blokzijl. "Free Email Client".  ''pcmagazine.zdnet.nl''.  CBS Interactive.  1 May 2006.  Retrieved at <http://pcmagazine.zdnet.nl/reviews/56115/foxmail-5-0-8/ {{Wayback|url=http://pcmagazine.zdnet.nl/reviews/56115/foxmail-5-0-8/ |date=20110824042645 }}> on 2 June 2011. (Belgian-Dutch)</ref>。

Foxmail 5在主题和地址头字段中放入了8位字符，违反了RFC 822、2822和5322{{Citation needed|date=June 2011}}，但是是为了支持[[IETF|IETF]]于2003年3月发布的RFC3454、RFC3490、RFC3491、RFC3492等[[中文域名协调联合会|中文域名标准]]<ref>"FAQ for Chinese Domain Name". ''cnnic.net.cn''.  China Internet Network Information Center.  10 October 2005.  Retrieved at <http://www.cnnic.net.cn/html/Dir/2005/10/11/3218.htm {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnnic.net.cn/html/Dir/2005/10/11/3218.htm |date=20110520143519 }}> on 2 June 2011.</ref>。

